channel.title: InvictusX Beta
channel.description:
Friendly Community I would like this RSPS to be know for a great and friendly community! What this means is for all players new and old to feel welcome and comfortable with all the players and staff! Staff will help maintain this peace. These staff will be personly chosen by me and the players/community will have a big say in the staff! Thanks and a warm welcome to all new players! Please communicate to use with the "Contact Us" Tab or talk to us on the fourms! Great Customs and Home! Picture YouTube Event Since this is a Brand new Rsps i Have decided to hold a competition for you people who are talented at making amazing Video's! Since these video represents this server I figured the video must be as great as the Rsps! If your video gets 125 views you will be rewarded with a YouTube cape! A custom cape made just for your YouTube talent and this even : ) ! Please send the video link on contact form and put the subject as "YouTube event"! Thank you and welcome to you who are new to our Rsps!
Website: http://rsps-invictusx.weebly.com/ DL link: https://www.dropbox.com/s/3kjxkkyhfvve601/Client.jar?dl=1
